(40, 22, 11, 58, 4, 12, 13, 'not on a wedding garment', 'Discerning the Unprepared', 'This connection highlights the theme of being unprepared for God''s judgment. Both passages emphasize the need for readiness and the revealing nature of God''s scrutiny.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 11, 45, 13, 14, 14, 'not on a wedding garment', 'Thematic Connection of Garments', 'This connection highlights the importance of being properly attired in a spiritual sense. Both passages emphasize the necessity of putting on a suitable garment, whether it be a wedding garment or the Lord Jesus Christ.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 11, 49, 4, 24, 24, 'not on a wedding garment', 'Connection of Righteousness and Garments', 'This connection highlights the importance of being properly attired in righteousness. Both passages emphasize the necessity of putting on a suitable garment, whether it be a wedding garment or the new man created in righteousness.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 11, 51, 3, 10, 11, 'not on a wedding garment', 'Connection of Garments and Identity', 'This connection highlights the importance of being properly attired in a spiritual sense. Both passages emphasize the necessity of putting on a new identity in Christ, contrasting the lack of a wedding garment with the renewal of the new man.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 9, 2, 9, 9, 'he was speechless', 'Silence of the Unprepared', 'This connection highlights the theme of being speechless or silent in the presence of judgment. In Matthew, the man is ''speechless'' when confronted about his lack of a wedding garment, while in 1 Samuel, the wicked are described as ''silent in darkness'' before God''s judgment.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 18, 5, 16, 16, 'not having a wedding garment', 'Hope and Accountability in Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability in faith. In Matthew, the man is questioned for not having a wedding garment, while in Job, the poor have hope, suggesting that iniquity can silence those unprepared or lacking righteousness.', 'theme', 0.349, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 40, 20, 13, 13, 'Friend', 'Friendship and Accountability', 'Both passages emphasize the term ''Friend,'' highlighting a relationship that involves accountability. In Matthew 22:12, the friend is questioned for not wearing a wedding garment, while in Matthew 20:13, the friend defends his actions regarding an agreement.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 19, 107, 42, 42, NULL, 'Righteousness and Accountability', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability in both passages. In Matthew, the man is questioned for not having a wedding garment, while in Psalms, iniquity is silenced, suggesting a contrast between righteousness and unpreparedness.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 24, 2, 23, 23, NULL, 'Connection of Accountability and Purity', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability for one''s actions and the necessity of being properly prepared. Both passages emphasize the importance of being in the right state, whether through a wedding garment or purity from idolatry.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 40, 26, 50, 50, 'Friend', 'Addressing the ''Friend'' Theme', 'Both passages emphasize the term ''Friend'' as Jesus addresses individuals in significant moments. This connection highlights the contrast between acceptance and accountability in their respective contexts.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 12, 44, 5, 2, 11, NULL, 'Consequences of Deception', 'Both passages emphasize the severe consequences of failing to meet expectations set by God. In Matthew, the man without a wedding garment is cast out for not being properly attired, while in Acts, Ananias and Sapphira face death for lying to the Holy Spirit.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
