(40, 22, 13, 40, 25, 30, 30, 'outer darkness; there shall be weeping and gnashing of teeth', 'Outer Darkness and Weeping', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of punishment in ''outer darkness'' and the resulting ''weeping and gnashing of teeth.'' This connection highlights a consistent portrayal of judgment for unworthy individuals in the context of the kingdom.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 13, 42, 13, 28, 28, 'weeping and gnashing of teeth', 'Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth', 'Both passages emphasize the phrase ''weeping and gnashing of teeth,'' indicating a state of regret and exclusion from the kingdom of God. This connection highlights the consequences faced by those who are cast out.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 22, 13, 53, 1, 9, 9, 'outer darkness', 'Punishment and Outer Darkness', 'Both passages emphasize punishment and separation from God. The ''outer darkness'' in Matthew parallels the ''everlasting destruction'' in 2 Thessalonians, highlighting the consequences of rejection.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
